channel.title: Nubia - Runescape front page themed skin design by S.U.N
channel.description:
OK don't lock my thread fir that comment i replied to cumescape, lol it was funny to me I think. At least edit post but hey I want him to see it, not as an insult or anything lol. We m8s tbh.
Hiiiiiiiiiiiiiii allllll, I'm back from being pissed and I gotten my mind refreshed, so I did this design. I'm going to code it soon and put it on my portfolio :D. By the way I never did let you guys see the site I finished, you can find it by [url=http://jarod-billingslea.freehostia.com/portfolio.php?]clicking here[/url] (click the preview link - its free for download :D). [u][b]About This[/b][/u] I always wanted to make a Runescape themed website that really took on competition of previous web designers. One of the main motivations for this idea was that there was not one design out yet that I think came close to the latest design of Runescape, I'm probably one of the few people to design a website close to Runescape's hah. The Inspiration came from WoW website designs, I'm kind of mad at the fact that Runescape web designs aren't in competition with WoW web designers at all (hardly touched to be honest). Took me about 5-8 hours to do this because I redid some parts back to back all day long. [center][url=http://rodsgfx.deviantart.com/art/Runescape-Themed-Web-Design-126335869]View Design[/url] Rate & comment! [b]Other pages soon to come too :D[/b][/center]
